      "author": "leotomhal",
      "description": "### Internal (grrrr)\r\n- Fixed the root cause of the type-safety warnings reported by Obsidian's review of 1.2.2: `tsconfig.json` declared an outdated `lib` (ES5–ES7), which made `padStart`, `Object.entries`, `flatMap`, and `Promise.finally` resolve as error-typed in the review environment. The lib is now ES2020, matching the compile target and Obsidian 1.7.2's runtime. No code changes; the bundle is unchanged.\r\n- Replaced the deprecated `builtin-modules` dev dependency with Node's built-in `builtinModules` from `node:module` in the esbuild config.",
