      "author": "leotomhal",
      "description": "## Changed\r\n\r\n- **Safer auto-cleanup:** completed tasks removed by the auto-delete setting are now archived to a `… (archive).md` note next to your tasks file before deletion. If that archive can't be written, nothing is deleted.\r\n\r\n## Internal\r\n\r\n- Added an automated test suite for the task-line parse/serialize round-trip, plus CI that runs it on every push and pull request — the part of the plugin that writes to your file is now covered by tests.\r\n\r\n**Full changelog:** https://github.com/leotomhal/sector-tasks-obsidian/compare/0.26.0...0.27.0",
